      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not a break though. a break implies i have something to come back to. but when i sit there, i just feel like the well is dry. like the person who used to create those things is actually dead, and this is just an empty shell dragging itself through the days. what's the point of keeping the lights on if there's nothing left to see? it just feels heavy. like a burden.",
